Introduction

This is a generated document for the Turnagain Arm area. The property tax information data from March 2016 was joined with the geographical parcel data in the Anchorage area and filtered for only parcels within the borders of Turnagain Arm community council.

This document was created to demostrate some of the skils of my business, Alaska Statistical Automation. If you have a project that might be an interesting project I would love to hear about it. Email me at hans.thompson1@gmail.com. I’m located in downtown Anchorage.

This document is provided for fun only and should not be used in investment decisions. If you would like to use this data for a futher analysis of investment opportunities, please get in contact! (hans.thompson1@gmail.com)

If you feel there is an interesting visualization that could be done with this information that could add to this report please let me know and I would be happy to try and include it across all areas.

Summary

The Turnagain Arm area contains 251 residential parcels and 16 non residential parcels. The total taxable residential value of land is $25,134,900 and the total taxable building value is $29,733,200.
The median taxable value for land and structures is $156,700
